listings.title: ✮✮✮Safe neighborhood, close to SF State & Stonestown✮✮✮
listings.description:
QR Code Link to This Post
            
        
Cozy 2 bedroom in-law with private entrance and laundry! 

What does this home offer:

➜Recently remodeled
➜ 2 bedrooms 
➜ Eat-in kitchen
➜ 1 modern updated bathroom
➜ Hardwood floors throughout the unit
➜ Lots of closets and storage spaces in the hallway
➜ Washer and dryer in unit (not coin operated!) ✓✓✓
➜ Very easy street parking 

What do you need around your home:

➜Close to public transportation (M-Line, 28 line)
➜Safe neighborhood 
➜Super Convenient (walking distance to Stonestown, gym, Trader Joe's, endless boba drinks & snacks, coffee shops, trendy and delicious restaurants)
➜Less than a block away from Stern Grove and close to Lake Merced - great places to picnic, hike, run, get your exercise on!

Monthly Rent $2200
Security Deposit: 2x rent
Utilities - tenant responsibility.
No pets. 
No smoking of any kind.


★★★Please email with an introduction about yourself and potential housemates and include links to your LinkedIn profiles to make an appointment for viewing. 
Thank you for your interest!
